    { name: 'Data reservoir architecture', filed: '041826 02:30', note: 'Caching proxy on FAS drive for bandwidth-disciplined bulk transfers (CUBE Win10 22H2 upgrade, future Android Blender build, fleet-wide OS updates). Station-agnostic, 8th-principle-compliant. Design pass: proxy software (squid / nginx caching / apt-cacher-ng), which FAS drive, cache invalidation, station configuration. Prefer caching-proxy over IP-forwarding-through-GOG1 (which couples fleet to one station).' },
